{"text_id":114370,"tokens":["In"," this"," work",","," we"," aim"," to"," de","construct"," functions"," on"," quadratic"," surfaces"," into"," multip","oles",","," thereby"," simplifying"," the"," analysis"," of"," complex"," systems","."," The"," problem"," we"," address"," is"," the"," difficulty"," in"," understanding"," and"," manipulating"," functions"," defined"," on"," quadratic"," surfaces",","," such"," as"," ellips","oids",","," parab","olo","ids",","," and"," hyper","bolo","ids",","," due"," to"," their"," intricate"," geometric"," structures","."," The"," motivation"," for"," our"," research"," is"," the"," potential"," of"," this"," approach"," to"," provide"," a"," more"," straightforward"," method"," for"," studying"," and"," designing"," systems"," that"," involve"," quadratic"," surfaces",","," such"," as"," those"," found"," in"," physics",","," computer"," graphics",","," and"," engineering",".","\n\n","Our"," research"," is"," based"," on"," the"," concept"," of"," multi","pole"," expansions",","," which"," are"," used"," to"," simplify"," the"," analysis"," of"," functions"," with"," radial"," symmetry","."," We"," extend"," this"," concept"," to"," functions"," on"," quadratic"," surfaces",","," defining"," multip","oles"," as"," function"," components"," that"," capture"," local"," behavior"," around"," specific"," points","."," We"," then"," develop"," a"," systematic"," method"," for"," decom","posing"," functions"," into"," these"," multip","oles",","," enabling"," the"," analysis"," of"," complex"," functions"," through"," the"," study"," of"," simpler",","," localized"," components",".","\n\n","The"," results"," obtained"," from"," our"," work"," show"," that"," the"," multi","pole"," decomposition"," of"," functions"," on"," quadratic"," surfaces"," is"," not"," only"," possible"," but"," also"," provides"," significant"," computational"," advantages"," over"," traditional"," methods","."," We"," demonstrate"," that"," this"," decomposition"," can"," be"," used"," for"," efficient"," function"," approximation",","," sampling",","," and"," compression","."," Additionally",","," we"," provide"," examples"," of"," its"," application"," to"," physical"," systems",","," such"," as"," gravitational"," potentials"," and"," electrostatic"," fields",","," further"," illustrating"," its"," potential"," for"," practical"," use",".","\n\n","In"," conclusion",","," our"," work"," on"," de","constru","cting"," functions"," on"," quadratic"," surfaces"," into"," multip","oles"," offers"," a"," powerful"," new"," tool"," for"," the"," analysis"," and"," design"," of"," complex"," systems",","," paving"," the"," way"," for"," future"," research"," in"," this"," field","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"mixtral-8x7b","label":1}